'''1N400x二极管'''（又称1N4001或1N4000{{notetag|值得注意的是，有文献将1N400x称为“1N4000二极管”。但1N4000本身是一款10 V[[齐纳二极管|齐纳稳压二极管]]的型号，和1N400x系列通用二极管无关<ref name="Motorola-1965"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.microsemi.com/existing-parts/parts/2548#overview|title=1N4000|website=[[Microsemi|Microsemi]]|access-date=2020-01-14|archive-date=2020-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200114153128/https://www.microsemi.com/existing-parts/parts/2548#overview|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此不建议使用该称呼。}}二极管）是型号为1N4001至1N4007的一系列通用硅[[二极管|二极管]]，其额定电流为1 A，反向耐压范围在50 V（1N4001）至1000 V（1N4007）之间，采用[[通孔插装技术|通孔插装]]式[[DO-41|DO-41]][[半导体封装|封装]]。<ref name="Vishay_1N4001_Datasheet"/><ref name="ON_1N4001_Datasheet"/>而1N540x二极管和1N400x相似，但额定电流提升至3 A，适合大功率的电器设备使用，封装采用尺寸更大的DO-201AD加强散热。<ref name="Vishay_1N5400_Datasheet"/><ref name="ON_1N5400_Datasheet"/>除了最常用的两者外，也有公司生产额定电流更高<ref name="Rectron_6A05_Datasheet"/>或者采用SMA和MELF等[[表面安装技术|表面安装技术]]（SMT）封装<ref name="Diotec_M1_Datasheet"/><ref name="Diotec_SM4001_Datasheet"/>的其他替代型号，详见下表。

自1963年由[[摩托罗拉|摩托罗拉]]推出以来<ref name="EIA-1963">{{cite web |title=Announcement of Electron Device Type Registration, Release No. 4190. |publisher=The Joint Electron Device Engineering Council |date=1963-03-18 |access-date=2019-01-22 |url=https://standards.globalspec.com/std/862253/eia-1n4001-1n4007 |archive-date=2020-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901091555/https://standards.globalspec.com/std/862253/eia-1n4001-1n4007 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1N400x系列二极管是[[电子工业|电子工业]]中特别常用的二极管型号<ref>{{cite book |title = The robot builder's bonanza |edition = 2nd |author = Gordon McComb |publisher = McGraw-Hill Professional |year = 2001 |isbn = 978-0-07-136296-2 |page = 41 |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=vYxRVw955-oC&pg=PA41 |quote = Common diodes are the 1N914, for light-duty signal-switching applications, and the 1N4000 series (1N4001, 1N4002, 1N4003, and 1N4004).}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |title = Home power, Issues 21–32 |publisher = Electron Connection, Ltd. |year = 1991 |page = 173 |url = https://books.google.com/?id=G2tQAAAAYAAJ&q=1N4000-series&dq=1N4000-series |quote = A good generic diode for 1 A or less is the 1N4000 series devices.}}</ref>，使用十分广泛，常在各类电器的[[交流適配器|交流电源适配器]]中用作[[整流器|整流器]]。<ref name=timothy-1992">
{{cite book |title = Electricity: fundamental concepts and applications |author = Timothy J. Maloney |publisher = Delmar Publishers |year = 1992 |isbn = 978-0-8273-4675-8 |page = 404 |url = https://books.google.com/?id=WkO_3P01a5MC&q=1N4004+popular&dq=1N4004+popular |quote = A Type No. 1N4004 diode, a popular diode for rectifying ac to dc.}}</ref>

== 历史 ==

1N400x系列二极管最初于1963年由[[摩托罗拉|摩托罗拉]]半导体产品部门推出，并在[[JEDEC|JEDEC]]进行了型号登记（Type Registration），记录中的产品类型为“用于工业或军事应用的电源硅整流器”。<ref name="EIA-1963">{{cite web| title=Announcement of Electron Device Type Registration, Release No. 4190. |publisher=The Joint Electron Device Engineering Council |date=1963-03-18 |access-date=2019-01-22 |url=https://standards.globalspec.com/std/862253/eia-1n4001-1n4007}}</ref>1965年的摩托罗拉《半导体数据手册》出现了该型号，并取代了较旧的1N2609至1N2617二极管。<ref name="Motorola-1965"/>

1968年，1N540x系列二极管上市，发售公告刊登在同年的《电子设计新闻》杂志（现{{link-en|EDN杂志|EDN (magazine)}}）。同时上市的还有已不常用的，额定电流为1.5 A的1N5391系列。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=JFNAAQAAIAAJ&q=1N5400&dq=1N5400 Electrical Design News], Volume 13, 1968</ref>

== 简介 ==

该系列二极管常在各类电器的[[交流適配器|交流电源适配器]]中用作[[整流器|整流器]]，将交流电转换为直流电（见下图）<ref name=timothy-1992"/>，也用于[[逆变器|逆变器]]等其他电源转换器，或者作为防止感性负载烧毁电路的[[续流二极管|续流二极管]]。<ref name="Vishay_1N4001_Datasheet"/>但该系列二极管的开关速度极低，工作频率超过15 kHz（方波）时性能就会无法令人接受<ref>{{citation |title=none|journal=[[Wireless_World|Wireless World]] |volume=88 |page=75 |year=1982}}</ref>，而一些数据手册中甚至根本没有导通时间和关断时间的任何信息<ref>{{cite book|title=Robust Electronic Design Reference Book|author=John R. Barnes|year=2004|page=15-9|quote=Earlier I mentioned that 1N4004's are rectifiers. They don't have any specfications in their datasheet for turn-on or turn-off characteristics.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DM6jcvOLZyoC&q=1N4004|access-date=2020-09-29|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930215055/https://books.google.com/books?id=DM6jcvOLZyoC&q=1N4004|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不适合用在开关类电路。作为一种功率二极管，其较高的反向漏电流和结电容也不适合小信号应用。<ref name=AOFE89>Paul Horowitz, Winifred Hill, ''The Art of Electronics Second Edition'', Cambridge University Press, 1989 {{ISBN|0-521-37095-7}}, page 330</ref>

